com/cablechinadesk/videos/1608827989261681/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2F&d=%2F3u2QRHOOrReLkGe8io5fW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=48582777\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://izquotes.com/quotes-pictures/quote-history-repeats-itself-first-as-tragedy-second-as-farce-karl-marx-120957.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fizquotes.com%2Fquotes-pictures%2Fquote-history-repeats-itself-first-as-tragedy-second-as-farce-karl-marx-120957.jpg&h=ad757ffe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雜種的霧月十八就快上演<br />\n似乎會幾搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f1bc5898a0b20209f1248701153250bbb7a5278","tid":526720,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T02:00:35.000Z","msg":"#修改錯誤歷史就可以令歷史變得更完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde231fd99f27c54d300af16eb387014176af2ba","tid":526720,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T02:01:54.000Z","msg":"真理部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eccf829030fc278f3b62cd19b8379e1afbab27c6","tid":526720,"uid":39974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T02:02:59.000Z","msg":"有線中國組又玩命"},{"pid":"e1dab6d83a66f4f63dea774cf1a80469a5b62cba","tid":526720,"uid":19093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"054e85c8f5d07fd3e184a449fb122ece53fa19f2","tid":526720,"uid":133529,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T01:41:46.000Z","msg":"支那仲好意思話日本。西毛個文革死人仲多過南京大屠殺，一撚樣咁冇人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T02:07:1