By":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T03:14:16.000Z","msg":"篡改歷史！"},{"pid":"d4aa9a9c4ba0b651b9f6af62d8011633b5b03fb5","tid":526720,"uid":126175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T03:15:32.000Z","msg":"日本侵華 南京大屠殺 令中國歷史更完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5091b3f99ca6d193dc703b450d55a2f6d45fc718","tid":526720,"uid":121409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T03:21:44.000Z","msg":"「人世間沒有一帆風順的事業，世界歷史總是在跌宕起伏的曲折過程中前進的」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n教科書用d咁感情色彩ge言詞<br />\n寫小說咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"badc91fcd87f32755a7eb040943047ad1dbfc149","tid":526720,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T03:23:40.000Z","msg":"掩耳盜鈴"}]}